overview: This is the story of Monica who is the newest super model of the year, but will she be able to cope with her newfound stardom? Being under the spotlight all the time, the parties, the orgies, the wild nightlife? It might all prove to be too much for this young girl. After disappearing one morning after a passionate sex session with her agent Paul, everyone begins a hot and torrid search for Monica. Where is she hiding and why?
title: Discovering Priva
